==Translingual==

===Alternative forms===
* In all regions except Taiwan, the middle right component is written as {{l|mul|日}}, which is the historical form found in the [[w:Kangxi Dictionary|Kangxi Dictionary]].
* In Taiwan, the middle right component is written as {{l|mul|白}} instead.
* In all regions except South Korea, the top right component is written similar to {{l|mul|小}} with a middle vertical stroke without ending hook ({{l|mul|丨}} instead of usual {{l|mul|亅}})
* In South Korea, the top right component is written as {{l|mul|小}} with a middle vertical stroke that has an ending hook ({{l|mul|亅}}).

