Possibly related to {{och-l|間|space, gap}} ({{zh-ref|Wang, 1982}}).

Outside of Chinese, compare {{cog|tbq-kuk-pro|*kak||to crack; to rend; to split}}, {{cog|kac|tr=kaʔ³¹|t=to crack}} ({{zh-ref|Sagart, 2017}}).

